539
00:29:49.913 --> 00:29:51.289
Yes. I do.

540
00:29:52.499 --> 00:29:54.375
Seriously. come.

541
00:29:56.377 --> 00:29:57.587
It'd be nice having you there.

542
00:29:59.547 --> 00:30:00.632
Thank you.

543
